{"TopicId":166121,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Ground Proximity warning","CreatedByName":"OperationDx","CreatedById":33950,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-03T17:43:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"OperationDx","CreatedById":33950,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-03T17:43:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know of a mod that has a ground proximity warning system?\u00A0 The Mod I found is outdated but I really like the concept found here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8753528560\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73776-12-proximity-audio-alarm-landing-aid/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo offence to the mod developer of GPWS which is updated to 1.3.\u00A0 I like the other one better.\u00A0 I just looking for all the options for this type of mod updated to the latest version of KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4726091634\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/101297-wip13gpws-warning-system-for-planes-2017-05-27/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:231px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for your help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-03T17:49:14Z\u0022 title=\u002210/03/2017 05:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 3, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by OperationDx\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiniMatt","CreatedById":78749,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-03T18:32:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not the laser focused streamlined option I sense you\u0027re after, but \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/17833-130-kerbal-engineer-redux-1130-2017-05-28/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbal Engineer Redux\u003C/a\u003E has - among its multitude of other features - a terrain altimeter. The HUD overlay can be customised to just about any requirements, including height, and vertical/horizontal velocity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tyko","CreatedById":164179,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-03T19:03:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnot sure about an audible alarm, but \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/126111-13-betterburntime-v16-accurate-burn-time-indicator-on-navball-no-more-na/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EBetter Burn Time\u003C/a\u003E has a readout that only comes up when it detects you\u0027re on a landing flight profile and tells time to impact and estimates your necessary burn time. I find it really useful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-03T19:22:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDanger alerts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7327247666\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/157835-13-danger-alerts-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-03T19:24:01Z\u0022 title=\u002210/03/2017 07:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 3, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by linuxgurugamer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-03T19:26:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving to Add-on Discussions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I was going to mention BetterBurnTime, except \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/164179-tyko/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022164179\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/164179-tyko/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Tyko\u003C/a\u003E beat me to it.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OperationDx","CreatedById":33950,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-04T06:26:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks everyone.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}